docstring:
Collates this iterable into sub-lists of length <code>size</code>.
Example:
<pre class="groovyTestCase">def list = [ 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7 ]
def coll = list.collate( 3 )
assert coll == [ [ 1, 2, 3 ], [ 4, 5, 6 ], [ 7 ] ]</pre>

